title: This is a correction, says TD Ameritrade's JJ Kinahan
text:
This is a correction, says TD Ameritrade's JJ Kinahan   04:31 
''The stock plunge on Monday is a correction, but it remains to be seen if this is the end of it or if it continues further,'' says JJ Kinahan, chief market strategist and managing director at TD Ameritrade. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
